  <entry>
    <title>Hexo+Github搭建个人静态博客</title>
    <url>/2021/10/18/Hexo+Github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-安装环境"><a href="#1-安装环境" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装环境"></a>1. 安装环境</h2><p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">Hexo官方中文文档</a></p>
<h3 id="1-1-准备"><a href="#1-1-准备" class="headerlink" title="1.1 准备"></a>1.1 准备</h3><ul>
<li>git</li>
<li>node.js</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="1-2-安装hexo"><a href="#1-2-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="1.2 安装hexo"></a>1.2 安装hexo</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="2-新建本地站点"><a href="#2-新建本地站点" class="headerlink" title="2. 新建本地站点"></a>2. 新建本地站点</h2><p>代码存放在 <code>G:\workspace\hexo</code>，在该目录下运行</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line">cd blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>目录文件：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">目录名称</th>
<th align="left">说明</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">scaffolds</td>
<td align="left">模版 文件夹。当您新建文章时，Hexo 会根据 scaffold 来建立文件。 Hexo的模板是指在新建的markdown文件中默认填充的内容。例如，如果您修改scaffold/post.md中的Front-matter内容，那么每次新建一篇文章时都会包含这个修改。</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">source</td>
<td align="left">资源文件夹是存放用户资源的地方。除 _posts 文件夹之外，开头命名为 _ (下划线)的文件 / 文件夹和隐藏的文件将会被忽略。Markdown 和 HTML 文件会被解析并放到 public 文件夹，而其他文件会被拷贝过去。</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">themes</td>
<td align="left">主题 文件夹。Hexo 会根据主题来生成静态页面。</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">_config.yml</td>
<td align="left">网站的 配置 信息，您可以在此配置大部分的参数。</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">package.json</td>
<td align="left">应用程序的信息。EJS, Stylus 和 Markdown renderer 已默认安装，您可以自由移除。</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="3-配置Hexo"><a href="#3-配置Hexo" class="headerlink" title="3. 配置Hexo"></a>3. 配置Hexo</h2><p>_config.yml为主要配置文件，一份位于站点根目录下，称为<strong>站点配置文件</strong>；一份位于主题目录下，称为<strong>主题配置文件</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo</span><br><span class="line">└── blog</span><br><span class="line">    ├── ...</span><br><span class="line">    ├── _config.yml  # 站点配置文件</span><br><span class="line">    └── themes</span><br><span class="line">        ├── ...</span><br><span class="line">        └── next</span><br><span class="line">            ├── ...</span><br><span class="line">            └── _config.yml  # 主题配置文件 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="3-1-替换主题"><a href="#3-1-替换主题" class="headerlink" title="3.1 替换主题"></a>3.1 替换主题</h3><p>安装主题Next，推荐使用git，方便后续更新</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git clone https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 使用主题，在站点配置文件中\hexo\blog\_config.yml中</span><br><span class="line">theme: next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>安装插入图片的插件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-asset-image --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 启用插件，在站点配置文件中\hexo\blog\_config.yml中</span><br><span class="line">post_asset_folder: true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 新增博文后，会在D:\hexo\blog\source\_posts目录下生成 xxx.md 和 xxx 目录，需要将图片存放 xxx 目录中，使用格式为 ![](***.jpg)，这样Typora预览和发布到网上时Hexo博客都能正常显示图片</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-2-本地预览"><a href="#3-2-本地预览" class="headerlink" title="3.2 本地预览"></a>3.2 本地预览</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 新建文章</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo new page &quot;name&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 清除缓存</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 生成静态文件</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 启动本地服务器</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo server --debug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="3-3-站点配置文件"><a href="#3-3-站点配置文件" class="headerlink" title="3.3 站点配置文件"></a>3.3 站点配置文件</h3><p>基本配置，修改名称，作者，语言和时区等</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Site</span><br><span class="line">title: My Blog</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">description: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: amoryy</span><br><span class="line">language: en</span><br><span class="line">timezone: &#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-4-主题配置文件"><a href="#3-4-主题配置文件" class="headerlink" title="3.4 主题配置文件"></a>3.4 主题配置文件</h3><p>3.4.1 修改总样式</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Schemes</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Muse</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Gemini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3.4.2 个人链接</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">social:</span><br><span class="line">  GitHub: https://github.com/Ay1c || fab fa-github</span><br><span class="line">  #E-Mail: mailto:yourname@gmail.com || fa fa-envelope</span><br><span class="line">  #Weibo: https://weibo.com/yourname || fab fa-weibo</span><br><span class="line">  #Google: https://plus.google.com/yourname || fab fa-google</span><br><span class="line">  #Twitter: https://twitter.com/yourname || fab fa-twitter</span><br><span class="line">  #FB Page: https://www.facebook.com/yourname || fab fa-facebook</span><br><span class="line">  #StackOverflow: https://stackoverflow.com/yourname || fab fa-stack-overflow</span><br><span class="line">  #YouTube: https://youtube.com/yourname || fab fa-youtube</span><br><span class="line">  #Instagram: https://instagram.com/yourname || fab fa-instagram</span><br><span class="line">  #Skype: skype:yourname?call|chat || fab fa-skype</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3.4.3 设置菜单，添加分类和标签</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: / || fa fa-home</span><br><span class="line">  #about: /about/ || fa fa-user</span><br><span class="line">  tags: /tags/ || fa fa-tags</span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories/ || fa fa-th</span><br><span class="line">  archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">  #schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar</span><br><span class="line">  #sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap</span><br><span class="line">  #commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 source 目录下新建页面 tags categories和 about</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># cmd</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page about</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在新生成的 <code>tags/index.md</code> 中添加 <code>type</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-10-15 17:12:15</span><br><span class="line">type: tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在文章中添加 tag</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 什么是Markdown</span><br><span class="line">date: 2021-10-15 11:19:19</span><br><span class="line">tags: [test]</span><br><span class="line">categories: [test]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3.4.4 添加搜索功能<br>安装插件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>修改站点配置文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#next search</span><br><span class="line">search:  </span><br><span class="line">    path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">    field: post</span><br><span class="line">    format: html</span><br><span class="line">    limit: 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>修改主题配置文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
